biography.bio: José Moratalla was born on December 23, 1941 in Sisante, Cuenca, Spain. He is known for his work on David the Gnome (1985), Dogtanian and the Three Muskehounds (1981) and Amor casi... libre (1976). He died on December 28, 1989 in Spain.
biography.name: José Moratalla

biography.bio: Fernando Vallejo is an actor, known for El golfo que vio una estrella (1955), Les tueurs de Madrid (1950) and Hospital of Urgency (1956).
biography.name: Fernando Vallejo

biography.birthName: Isabel María Bastos Osorio de Castro e Oliveira
biography.bio: Isabel de Castro was born on August 1, 1931 in Lisbon, Portugal as Isabel María Bastos Osorio de Castro e Oliveira. She was an actress, known for A Grande Aposta (1997), Anjo Selvagem (2001) and Desencontros (1994). She was married to Carlos Otero, Óscar Acúrcio and Miguel Luke. She died on November 23, 2005 in Borba, Portugal.
biography.name: Isabel de Castro

biography.bio: Miguel Gila was born on March 12, 1919 in Madrid, Spain as Miguel Gila Cuesta. He was an actor and writer, known for El hombre que viajaba despacito (1957), El ceniciento (1955) and ¿De parte de quién? (1993). He was married to Maria Dolores Cobo. He died on July 13, 2001 in Barcelona, Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain.
biography.name: Miguel Gila

biography.bio: Barta Barri was born on August 16, 1911 in Budapest, Austria-Hungary as Bernabé Barta Barry. He was an actor, known for Red Sun (1971), Horror Express (1972) and The Werewolf Versus the Vampire Woman (1971). He was married to Maria Cañete. He died on December 7, 2003 in Madrid, Spain.
biography.name: Barta Barri

biography.bio: Carlos Otero was born on May 30, 1916 in Lisbon, Portugal as Carlos Otero Dos Santos Pereira. He was an actor, known for Young Sánchez (1964), Hay un camino a la derecha (1953) and The Man in Hiding (1971). He was married to Isabel de Castro. He died on August 29, 1979 in Ibiza, Balearic Islands, Spain.
biography.name: Carlos Otero

biography.bio: José Sazatornil was born on August 13, 1925 in Barcelona, Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain as José Sazatornil Buendía. He was an actor, known for Amanece, que no es poco (1989), Todos a la cárcel (1993) and Attends-moi au ciel (1988). He was married to Carmen. He died on July 23, 2015 in Madrid, Madrid, Spain.
biography.name: José Sazatornil
